import { Box, Card, Grid } from '@mui/material'
import React from 'react'
import { theme } from '../theme/theme'

const Home = () => {
  return (
    <Box display={'flex'}>
      {/* 左側コンテンツ */}
      <Box flexGrow={1}>
        <Grid container spacing={2}>
          <Grid item xs={4}>
            <Card
              sx={{
                bgcolor: (theme) => theme.palette.goalColor.main,
                color: 'white',
                borderRadius: '10px',
                flexGrow: 1
              }}
            >aa</Card>
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={4}>
            
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={4}>
            
          </Grid>
        </Grid>
      </Box>
      {/* 右側コンテンツ */}
      <Box>
        
      </Box>
    </Box>
  )
}

export default Home
